text: Trying to get my 80yo mom 2nd Moderna dose in #California. What a mess. No appt for 2nd shot when she got 1st, now all appts booked. Website not intuitive. On hold w/ 211 half hour so far. How we’re expecting this population to navigate process is shameful. #vaccine #Covid19 https://t.co/O8i6YMYxwD
